cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.LG

This paper deals with image processing techniques for enhancing retinal fundus images for blood vessel segmentation. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves the evaluation of different enhancement techniques, which falls under the sub-category of information retrieval (cs.IR). The use of Hough line transformation for vessel reconstruction suggests the involvement of multimedia (cs.MM) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) techniques. Finally, the assessment of the proposed approach using different techniques involves machine learning (cs.LG) methods.
